title: Grateful Dead Live at Ventura County Fairgrounds on 1984-07-21
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi DR-1) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) >KORG AudioGate 4 > Adobe Audition 3.0 > FLAC/24
taper: Robert Bryant  (patched out of Oade Brothers)
description:
Set 1

Shakedown Street, Little Red Rooster, Althea, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider-> Looks Like Rain-> Might As Well

Set 2

Cold Rain & Snow-> Far From Me-> Truckin'-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> Around & Around-> One More Saturday Night, E: Touch Of Grey

reviews.review_text: Summer splendor This should be on everyone's short list of best shows of '84.
Marky Mark knows his shit! Ventura Olympic Gold right here. Next day was another 2 Medals!
